ike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fimages%2Fbasiclawtext_doc11.pdf&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8c41dd2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢件文件有晒香港土地範圍的經緯度<br />\n咁都可以話一地兩檢冇違反基本法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「文件十一」係支那宗主國既行政命令<br />\n技術上, 唔係《基本法》內容</blockquote><br />\n乜料呀⋯⋯<br />\n咁寫出來托?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫出黎呃傻仔</blockquote><br />\n過咗廿幾年 當年啲傻仔先發覺原來比人呃咗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本全香港都無人真係去研究過所謂《基本法》既問題<br />\n當年一味「回歸、回歸、回歸」high到上天"},{"pid":"98aa2e40c002e83c11e5d90b4e6386e22e582298","tid":336023,"uid":23993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fimages%2Fbasiclawtext_doc11.pdf&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8c41dd2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢件文件有晒香港土地範圍的經緯度<br />\n咁都可以話一地兩檢冇違反基本法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「文件十一」係支那宗主國既行政命令<br />\n技術上, 唔係《基本法》內容</blockquote><br />\n乜料呀⋯⋯<br />\n咁寫出來托?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫出黎呃傻仔</blockquote><br />\n過咗廿幾年 當年啲傻仔先發覺原來比人呃咗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本全香港都無人真係去研究過所謂《基本法》既問題<br />\n當年一味「回歸、回歸、回歸」high到上天</blockquote><br />\n基本法根本寫嚟係為咗授予人大對港管治最大權力<br />\n內容本身千疏百孔<br />\n仲要係有意為之方便人大未來按需要隨意加鹽加醋<br />\n當年啲傻仔至今仲奉基本法為聖旨 仲咁天真以為靠本嘢真係可以保自由民主法治 熱狗青城仲真係信靠本嘢可以保住層樓<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"84104810c276688fe89494b0fa1a4cbed7ab6dd7","tid":336023,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fimages%2Fbasiclawtext_doc11.pdf&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8c41dd2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢件文件有晒香港土地範圍的經緯度<br />\n咁都可以話一地兩檢冇違反基本法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「文件十一」係支那宗主國既行政命令<br />\n技術上, 唔係《基本法》內容</blockquote><br />\n乜料呀⋯⋯<br />\n咁寫出來托?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫出黎呃傻仔</blockquote><br />\n過咗廿幾年 當年啲傻仔先發覺原來比人呃咗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本全香港都無人真係去研究過所謂《基本法》既問題<br />\n當年一味「回歸、回歸、回歸」high到上天</blockquote><br />\n基本法根本寫嚟係為咗授予人大對港管治最大權力<br />\n內容本身千疏百孔<br />\n仲要係有意為之方便人大未來按需要隨意加鹽加醋<br />\n當年啲傻仔至今仲奉基本法為聖旨 仲咁天真以為靠本嘢真係可以保自由民主法治 熱狗青城仲真係信靠本嘢可以保住層樓<br />\n屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之極致囉<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》既重點係, 都無經過香港人公投, 無社會契約存在 <br />\n(《香港獨立論》觀點)<br />\n<br />\n熱普賤及中箭班on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住搞公投, 去補鑊公投呢本垃圾 (即變相公投統一), <br />\n20年後補返個社會契約, 點知依家呢本野越揭越垃圾<br />\n仲邊個會去搞公投統一？"},{"pid":"543a7fe9922f57992154ea6a671b506ef8903fc4","tid":336023,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f901e1128ab732ec07f97529ad6a6d88f4f3754","tid":336023,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"國務院令唔係基本法一部分，國務院可以想改就改，2015年國務院令第665號就重新定義左澳門界線，令澳門多左水域同關閘邊檢大樓。"},{"pid":"a547233ed0727e0af19beb6642d88dbcf89d32a8","tid":336023,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fimages%2Fbasiclawtext_doc11.pdf&d=R39rRjhGqRHJV8Ki76lo2qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8c41dd2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc11.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢件文件有晒香港土地範圍的經緯度<br />\n咁都可以話一地兩檢冇違反基本法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「文件十一」係支那宗主國既行政命令<br />\n技術上, 唔係《基本法》內容</blockquote><br />\n乜料呀⋯⋯<br />\n咁寫出來托?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫出黎呃傻仔</blockquote><br />\n過咗廿幾年 當年啲傻仔先發覺原來比人呃咗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本全香港都無人真係去研究過所謂《基本法》既問題<br />\n當年一味「回歸、回歸、回歸」high到上天</blockquote><br />\n基本法根本寫嚟係為咗授予人大對港管治最大權力<br />\n內容本身千疏百孔<br />\n仲要係有意為之方便人大未來按需要隨意加鹽加醋<br />\n當年啲傻仔至今仲奉基本法為聖旨 仲咁天真以為靠本嘢真係可以保自由民主法治 熱狗青城仲真係信靠本嘢可以保住層樓<br />\n屌</blockquote><br />\n一直都話基本法保障支那有絕對控制權嘅嘢就好清晰<br />\n但保障香港獨特性嘅嘢就輕描淡寫"}]}